This paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques applied to biomedical literature for extracting Protein-Protein Interactions (PPIs). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which suggests the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which suggests the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
